# Build context for `containers/ci/ubuntu.Dockerfile`.
#
# Only `containers/ci/sanity.sh` is COPY'd into the image; everything
# else in the repo is irrelevant for image build and would only inflate
# the build context (= slow `docker build`, large `docker save`).
#
# `*` first then `!`-allow the files we actually need.
*

# Keep the sanity check that the Dockerfile COPY'es in.
!containers/ci/sanity.sh
